name: Hawa Cat Sending Love to Planet GJ 504b
description: Hawa Cat is the wise kitten of pink plant GJ 504b. She's on vacation at the space station. She's thinking of GJ 504b & feeling so much love. Animated art.This space station is 1000 miles long and contains oceans, lakes  & agricultural quadrants. Original art in watercolor & ink by artist NFTeve Hennessa.
